gold.question: Which grade has the most high schoolers?
gold.sql_query: SELECT grade FROM Highschooler GROUP BY grade ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1
gold.answer: Grade 12 has the most high schoolers.

gold.question: What are the names of the dogs for which the owner has not spend more than 1000 for treatment ?
gold.sql_query: select name from dogs where dog_id not in ( select dog_id from treatments group by dog_id having sum(cost_of_treatment)  >  1000 )
gold.answer: The names of the dogs for which the owner has not spent more than 1000 for treatment are: Kacey, Hipolito, Mavis, Houston, Jeffrey, Merritt, Narciso, George, Bessie, Betty, Holden, and Jesus.

pred.question: What are the names of the dogs for which the owner has not spend more than 1000 for treatment ?
pred.sql_query: SELECT Dogs.name, SUM(Treatments.cost_of_treatment) as total_cost FROM Dogs JOIN Treatments ON Dogs.dog_id = Treatments.dog_id GROUP BY Dogs.dog_id HAVING total_cost <= 1000 ORDER BY total_cost DESC
pred.answer: The names of the dogs for which the owner has not spent more than 1000 for treatment are Narciso, Hipolito, Holden, Kacey, Jesus, and Houston.
